                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9637" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">SCLM-0255</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">698 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">从产业投资到数字化产业链金融：天奇股份产融结合实践</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">From industrial investment to digital industrial chain finance : Tianqi &#39;s practice of integration of industry and finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王琼，洪雨心，范文雯</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">合肥工业大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">天奇自动化工程股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">其他</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">综合管理部门/总经理办公室</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">15 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产业投资；供应链金融；供应链金融科技；数字化产业链金融</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Industrial investment ; supply chain finance ; supply chain financial technology ; industrial chain finance</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“新质生产力”被列入2024年政府工作十大任务之首，集成诸多新技术的新能源汽车产业无疑是发展新质生产力的重要着力点。锂离子电池是新能源汽车的“心脏”，伴随着新能源汽车的蓬勃发展及退役潮的来临，动力锂电池回收成为热门赛道。作为致力于服务汽车全生命周期的天奇股份正是锂电回收产业链的核心企业，天奇股份运用多元化的产融结合模式，从产业投资到供应链金融再到数字化产业链金融，逐步实现“科技—产业—金融”的良性循环，形成了具有“天奇特色”的锂电服务循环体系。本案例旨在全面梳理天奇股份探索锂电循环产业发展的产融结合实践，以引导学生在深入理解供应链金融、供应链金融科技、产业链金融等概念的基础上，全面掌握这些产融结合模式在天奇股份推动“科技—产业—金融”良性循环实践中的应用，并期待为其他产业的高质量发展提供借鉴。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">&#39;New quality productivity &#39; is listed as the top ten tasks of government work in 2024. The new energy automobile industry integrating many new technologies is undoubtedly an important focus for the development of new quality productivity. Lithium-ion battery is the &#39; heart &#39; of new energy vehicles. With the vigorous development of new energy vehicles and the advent of retirement tide, power lithium battery recycling has become a hot track. As a core enterprise dedicated to serving the whole life cycle of automobiles, Tianqi Co., Ltd.is the core enterprise of the lithium battery recycling industry chain. Tianqi Co., Ltd.uses a diversified combination of industry and finance, from industrial investment to supply chain finance to digital industry chain finance, and gradually realizes the virtuous cycle of &#39; technology industry finance &#39;, forming a lithium battery service cycle system with &#39; Tianqi characteristics &#39;. The purpose of this case is to comprehensively sort out the practice of Tianqi &#39;s exploration of</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2024</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《供应链金融》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">产融结合；供应链金融；供应链金融科技；产业链金融</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
